<h2 class="text-center">{l s='"General" tab' mod='cdek20'}</h2>
<hr>
<strong>{l s='Fields "Account" and "Password"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='You can get the data for these fields in the "Integration" tab in your personal SDEK account.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
{l s='If you do not have a personal CDEK account, then you need to register with CDEK and conclude an agreement.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Link to register with CDEK:' mod='cdek20'}
<strong><a href="https://lk.cdek.ru/user/login">{l s='lk.cdek.ru/user/login' mod='cdek20'}</a></strong><br>
{l s='Link to sign contract:' mod='cdek20'}
<strong><a href="https://cdek.ru/ru/contract">{l s='cdek.ru/ru/contract' mod='cdek20'}</a></strong><br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Yandex API key"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='An optional field to fill out.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Fill in only if the widget with the pickup points map will not work' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='The key can be obtained from the link:' mod='cdek20'}
<strong><a href="https://developer.tech.yandex.ru/services/3">{l s='developer.tech.yandex.ru/services/3' mod='cdek20'}</a></strong><br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Vendor"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Seller is company name. This field will be displayed in the CDEK invoice in the field "Seller"' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Sender" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='The name of the sender is company. This field will be displayed in the CDEK invoice and in the CDEK PA order.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Manager is name"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Enter the name of the contact person. This field will be displayed only in the order of LC SDEK.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Phone" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Enter phone number. Required when using delivery from the "door" to call the courier. This field will be displayed only in the order of LC SDEK.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Shipper is address" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Specify the address of the online store. Required for international deliveries.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "Contract currency"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='The currency that the online store uses to work with CDEK' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "VAT"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='The cost in CDEK will include VAT. Applies to shipping' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "Partial delivery"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='If you select "Yes", then the buyer, upon receipt of the order, will be able to refuse part of the goods.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "Each product in a separate position"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='If you select "Yes", then each item in the order will be in a separate position.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Example: if you bought one product in the amount of 10 pieces, then there will be 10 positions of this product' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "All products in one position"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Regardless of the number of products, all products will be combined and displayed as one product. Instead of the product name, there will be an order number' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Option "All products in one box" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Regardless of the quantity, weight and volume of goods, all goods will be transferred in one box' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
